ActCourts Administration Service Act
PrecisConfirm that RAYMOND P. GUENETTE of Ottawa, Ontario, a Deputy Chief Administrator, may continue to act as Chief Administrator of the Courts Administration Service, for the period commencing on December 4, 2006 until such time a new Chief Administrator is appointed.
